{"tid":1557913,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"一撚定要贏！9 月文宣行動POST！和理非同我入黎睇！！！","createTime":"2019-09-10T09:48:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T11:55:13.000Z","uid":20442,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8f76ca3a7bba6541ca82ab5643c5c88a1ee4c4aa","tid":1557913,"uid":20442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:48:53.000Z","msg":"開咗學，發現大量大陸、藍絲、犬二代完全唔知成個暑假發生咩事 ！ <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢地係住大陸，或者家人禁睇任何片、新聞</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來有堆初中、高小學生連TVB 都冇睇！ 甚至乎有啲大陸人覺得區區都係港獨，啲二代唔知<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警暴係咩事！活係平行時空！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">知道大家9 月好攰，但而家搵到新方向俾各位和理非出發進攻！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 朝早7點半學校叫口號5 分鐘！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 朝早文宣6-7 點貼滿連儂牆，7點至7 點半，社區播片、播精華片，例如：榮光歸香港🇭🇰<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好睇少啲跨境生、深藍二代，佢地日日出入兩地，人口又多，影響好大</span></span><br />\n既然開學了，我方係要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">輸出革命意志，重溫721、811、831，一個又一個事實！教導所有大陸雙單非、藍二代咩叫「法治」，咩係「人治」！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 校內，啲form4-6 、社長，唔該你地好好重溫2019 香港仲夏時事！！！可以有QRCode俾啲深度文章、港台片、血相俾啲師弟妹睇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國師、沈旭暉、19 才子陶傑、講人話時既敵營（曾鈺成）、香港首富李嘉誠，你估啲細路日日上連登呀？屌，我地要好好俾啲文宣、歌、理念、紀錄片、立場、蘋果圖片，佢地睇下</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.大量轉載，文宣蘋果、立場新聞、相片！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">佢地連學生人鏈，名校罷課都唔撚知呀！俾啲相佢地睇啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n發夢夢到：大埔、北區（上水、粉嶺）、元屯天遍地開花，唔該啲新界高中生係校內搞多啲時事分享！<br />\n香港十八區都有150 人，和理非一齊教教佢地啲二代，咩叫<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港精神，香港法治，咩叫港人自治！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做<br />\n<br />\n大人宣傳世界，細路宣傳藍二代、大陸二代！<br />\n寧鳴而死，不默而生<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2019 年9 月香港人唔會屈服俾垃圾權貴，拆一撕十，大家做野！</span></span>"},{"pid":"2226cc44649b086658a1f4f299cad8648a214bd1","tid":1557913,"uid":20442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:50:21.000Z","msg":"721 811 831"},{"pid":"4f9aefa49e9fff561f599ba226330a44f16eaf96","tid":1557913,"uid":20442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:51:04.000Z","msg":"721 811 831 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83dfc5e915aad202356cf3bfb23c37cb1919f3ef","tid":1557913,"uid":20442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:52:28.000Z","msg":"發夢聽到：有深藍二代初中生醞釀革命意志，因為睇咗好多街上文宣！！！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e19cdfe34761cac3579e58c8e0eb907b6a39e138","tid":1557913,"uid":20442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:53:24.000Z","msg":"721 811 831"},{"pid":"0cc08ce319260edd0adce66ed8f31b4831750c6f","tid":15